<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui"
	xmlns:d="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.datepicker.client">
	<ui:style src="DesktopStyles.css" />
	<ui:style field="otherStyles">
	</ui:style>
	<g:ScrollPanel width="99%" height="99%">
	<g:VerticalPanel spacing="8" width="100%">
		<g:HorizontalPanel ui:field="pleaseWaitPanel" width="100%" visible="false">
			<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_CENTER" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_MIDDLE">
				<g:VerticalPanel spacing="8">
					<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_CENTER" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_MIDDLE">
						<g:Image url="images/ajax-loader.gif"/>
					</g:cell>
					<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_CENTER" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_MIDDLE">
						<g:HTML ui:field="pleaseWaitHTML" addStyleNames="{style.body}"/>
					</g:cell>
				</g:VerticalPanel>
			</g:cell>
		</g:HorizontalPanel>
		<!-- 
SystemId?, ServiceNow internal id to uniquely identify a record in the custom table. Not required in create. Required for update/delete.  wsdl: sys_id
UserNetID, Form: requestor userID; wsdl: u_requested_for
ApplicationName,   Form: For what application is this firewall exception needed.  wsdl: u_common_name
IsSourceOutsideEmory,  Form:Is the source outside of Emory's network and the destination inside?.  Valid values: Yes, No.  wsdl: u_internet_access
TimeRule,  how long the firewall exception will be valid.  Valid values: Indefinitely, SpecificDate.  wsdl: u_how_long
ValidUntilDate?,  if ValidUntil is SpecificDate, this field holds the date string, such as 2018-11-14. wsdl: u_specific_date 
SourceIpAddresses,  Source IP addresses AND fully qualified domain names of the system(s) that need to access the destination(s).  wsdl: u_ip_address 
DestinationIpAddresses, Destination IP address(es) AND fully qualified domain name(s) of the system(s) that needs to be accessible through the firewall.  wsdl: u_ip_address2 
Ports,  Destination ports, applications, or services that need to be accessible. Indicate TCP or UDP for each, or ICMP type, along with the underlying protocol or application.  wsdl: u_ports 
BusinessReason, - Describe the business justification for this exception.  wsdl: u_business_reason 
IsPatched, - Are Server/Service/Application components fully patched at the time of this request?  valie values: Yes, No.  wsdl: u_patch_server 
IsDefaultPasswdChanged, - Have all default application or server passwords been changed? valid values: Yes, No.  wsdl: u_app_pswd 
IsAppConsoleACLed, - Have all administrative/management consoles for the application, as well as any underlying technology administrative/management consoles (such as ColdFusion, Jboss, Tomcat, phpmyadmin) been properly ACL'd. valid values: Yes, No. wsdl: u_mgmt_consol 
IsHardened, - Have hardening guidelines for the application/service and underlying technologies been followed and implemented? Valid values: Yes, No.  wsdl:  u_guidelines 
PatchingPlan, - Describe your plan for keeping this application/service and underlying technologies patched in a timely manner.  wsdl: u_plan 
Compliance*, - Is this application/service in scope of any of the following compliance regimes? valid values: FERPA, FISMA, HIPAA, PCI, Other, Unsure. wsdl: u_comp_1 to u_comp_6 
OtherCompliance?, - compliance description when the Compliance value is "Other".  wsdl: u_other_compliance 
SensitiveDataDesc, - Describe any sensitive data that will be stored or processed on this system.  wsdl: u_sensitivity 
LocalFirewallRules, - Describe any local (host-based) firewall rules that are currently configured on the system.  wsdl: u_firewall_rules 
IsDefaultDenyZone, - Could this system be placed into a subnet that blocks all outbound Internet traffic by default.  valid values: Yes, No.  wsdl: u_subnet 
Tag+, - tags for this request.  wsdl: u_tag
RequestNumber?,  - ServiceNow request number, generated by the create call internally.  wsdl: u_req_number 
RequestState?, - status of this request, updated by ServiceNow.  Valid values:Open, Pending, Work In Progress, Skip Task, Task Incomplete, Closed Complete.  wsdl: u_req_state 
RequestItemNumber?,  - ServiceNow request item number, generated by the create call internally.  wsdl: u_ritm_number 
RequestItemState?, - ServiceNow request item state, updated by ServiceNow request fulfillment.  This is the value that an application should check for Request state for custom requests. Valid values:Open, Pending, Work In Progress, Skip Task, Task Incomplete, Closed Complete.  wsdl: u_ritm_state.  This field has the actual fulfillment status for the firewall request 
CreateDateTime?,  - the date and time when the request is created.  Populated by SN.
UpdateDateTime? - the date and time when the request is updated, either by requestor or the fulfiller.  Populated by SN.
		 -->
		<g:HorizontalPanel>
		<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_LEFT" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_MIDDLE">
			<g:Grid cellSpacing="8">
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Requestor NetID:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextBox addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="netIdTB" debugId="netIdTB" />
				    </g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Technical Contact:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextBox addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="technicalContactTB" debugId="technicalContactTB" />
				    </g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Application Name:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextBox addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="applicationNameTB" debugId="applicationNameTB" 
							title="For what application is this firewall exception needed."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Source Outside Emory:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
				    	<g:CheckBox ui:field="isSourceOutsideEmoryCB" debugId="isSourceOutsideEmoryCB" 
				    		addStyleNames="{style.label}"
				    		title="Is the source outside of Emory's network and the destination inside?"/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Time Rule:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:ListBox addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="timeRuleLB" debugId="timeRuleLB" 
							title="how long the firewall exception will be valid."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
				</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label ui:field="validUntilLabel" addStyleNames="{style.label}">Valid Until Date:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<d:DateBox addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="validUntilDB"  debugId="validUntilDB"/>
				    </g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Source IP Addresses:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextArea addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="sourceIpAddressesTA" debugId="sourceIpAddressesTA" 
							title="Source IP addresses AND fully qualified domain names of the system(s) that need to access the destination(s)."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Destination IP Addresses:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextArea addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="destinationIpAddressesTA" debugId="destinationIpAddressesTA" 
							title="Destination IP address(es) AND fully qualified domain name(s) of the system(s) that needs to be accessible through the firewall."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Ports:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextArea addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="portsTA" debugId="portsTA" 
							title="Destination ports, applications, or services that need to be accessible. Indicate TCP or UDP for each, or ICMP type, along with the underlying protocol or application."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Business Reason:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextArea addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="businessReasonTA" debugId="businessReasonTA" 
							title="Describe the business justification for this exception."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Patched:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
				    	<g:CheckBox ui:field="isPatchedCB" debugId="isPatchedCB" addStyleNames="{style.label}"
				    		title="Are Server/Service/Application components fully patched at the time of this request?"/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Default Password Changed:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
				    	<g:CheckBox ui:field="isDefaultPasswordChangedCB" debugId="isDefaultPasswordChangedCB" 
				    		addStyleNames="{style.label}"
				    		title="Have all default application or server passwords been changed?"/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Consoles ACL'd:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
				    	<g:CheckBox ui:field="isAppConsoleACLedCB" debugId="isAppConsoleACLedCB" addStyleNames="{style.label}"
				    		title="Have all administrative/management consoles for the application, as well as any underlying technology administrative/management consoles (such as ColdFusion, Jboss, Tomcat, phpmyadmin) been properly ACL'd."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Hardened:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
				    	<g:CheckBox ui:field="isHardenedCB" debugId="isHardenedCB" addStyleNames="{style.label}"
				    		title="Have hardening guidelines for the application/service and underlying technologies been followed and implemented?"/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Patching Plan:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextArea addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="patchingPlanTA" debugId="patchingPlanTA" 
							title="Describe your plan for keeping this application/service and underlying technologies patched in a timely manner."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:HTML addStyleNames="{style.label}">Compliance Class<br></br>(select all):</g:HTML>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:ListBox multipleSelect="true" addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="complianceClassLB" debugId="complianceClassLB" 
							title="Is this application/service in scope of any of the following compliance regimes?"/>
			    	</g:customCell>
				</g:row>
				<!-- TODO: if compliance is 'Other' need to prompt for the value -->
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Sensitive Data Description:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextArea addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="sensitiveDataDescriptionTA" debugId="sensitiveDataDescriptionTA" 
							title="Describe any sensitive data that will be stored or processed on this system."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Local Firewall Rules:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:TextArea addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"
							ui:field="localFirewallRulesDescriptionTA" debugId="localFirewallRulesDescriptionTA" 
							title="Describe any local (host-based) firewall rules that are currently configured on the system."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.label}">Default Deny Zone:</g:Label>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
				    	<g:CheckBox ui:field="isDefaultDenyZoneCB" debugId="isDefaultDenyZoneCB" addStyleNames="{style.label}"
				    		title="Could this system be placed into a subnet that blocks all outbound Internet traffic by default."/>
			    	</g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
			</g:Grid>
		</g:cell>
		<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_LEFT" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_MIDDLE">
			<g:Grid cellSpacing="8">
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:HorizontalPanel>
							<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_LEFT" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_TOP" width="50%">
									<g:ScrollPanel>
										<g:VerticalPanel spacing="8" ui:field="tagsVP" height="100%">
											<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.heading_label}">Add/remove Tags:</g:Label>
											<g:HorizontalPanel ui:field="addTagHP" spacing="16">
												<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_LEFT" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_MIDDLE">
													<g:TextBox ui:field="addTagTF" debugId="addTagTF" addStyleNames="{style.field} {style.glowing-border}"></g:TextBox>
												</g:cell>
												<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_LEFT" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_MIDDLE">
													<g:Button ui:field="addTagButton" debugId="addTagButton"
														addStyleNames="{style.glowing-border} {style.actionButton}">Add</g:Button>
												</g:cell>
											</g:HorizontalPanel>
											<g:VerticalPanel spacing="8">
												<g:Label addStyleNames="{style.heading_label}">Tags associated to this Firewall Exception Request:</g:Label>
												<g:FlexTable ui:field="tagsTable" debugId="tagsTable" cellSpacing="3" cellPadding="3" title="Tags for this request."/>
											</g:VerticalPanel>
										</g:VerticalPanel>
									</g:ScrollPanel>
							</g:cell>
						</g:HorizontalPanel>
				    </g:customCell>
		    	</g:row>
		    </g:Grid>
		</g:cell>
		</g:HorizontalPanel>
		<g:cell horizontalAlignment="ALIGN_LEFT" verticalAlignment="ALIGN_MIDDLE" width="100%">
			<g:Grid cellSpacing="12">
				<g:row>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Button addStyleNames="{style.glowing-border} {style.normalButton}"
							ui:field="okayButton" debugId="okayButton">Save</g:Button>
			    	</g:customCell>
			    	<g:customCell>
						<g:Button addStyleNames="{style.glowing-border} {style.normalButton}"
							ui:field="cancelButton" debugId="cancelButton">Cancel</g:Button>
			    	</g:customCell>
				</g:row>
			</g:Grid>
		</g:cell>
	</g:VerticalPanel>
	</g:ScrollPanel>
</ui:UiBinder> 